{{ heading('Semantic text tokens', '3') }}

<p>Semantic text tokens reference the core font scales and give them purpose. Rather than applying raw scale values directly, semantic tokens map to the typescale variants used across Vivid — making it straightforward to apply consistent typography throughout the system.</p>
<p>Each typescale variant has it's own composite token eg. <code>text-heading-xl</code>, that is made up of the five key font scales to form one hand token.

